    _NET_WM_WINDOW_TYPE_DOCK
    Ewmh.hh/cc
  * Fixed so one can navigate in menu even if     (Henrik)
    numlock, capslock or scrollock are on
    Menu.cc
*04/01/19:
  * Fixed minor bug in ResourceManager (Henrik)
    Resource.cc
  * Support for:                   (Henrik)
